<div class="space-y-6">
  <!-- Overview -->
  <div class="nerv-panel">
    <div class="nerv-panel-header">
      <span>MAGI SYSTEM OVERVIEW</span>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6">
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-terminal-gray font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The <span class="text-terminal-cyan">MAGI Quality Assurance System</span> is a comprehensive test management platform designed for organizing, executing, and tracking software testing operations. The interface is inspired by the NERV command center aesthetic from Neon Genesis Evangelion.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="p-4 border border-terminal-cyan/30 bg-terminal-cyan/5">
            <h4 class="text-terminal-cyan font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Core Capabilities</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm font-mono text-terminal-gray space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-terminal-cyan">›</span>
                <span>Organize tests into Protocol Banks (Test Suites)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-terminal-cyan">›</span>
                <span>Define detailed test Protocols with steps and expected outcomes</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-terminal-cyan">›</span>
                <span>Execute Operations (Test Runs) and track results</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-terminal-cyan">›</span>
                <span>Monitor project progress via the Command Overview dashboard</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 border border-terminal-amber/30 bg-terminal-amber/5">
            <h4 class="text-terminal-amber font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Integration Features</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm font-mono text-terminal-gray space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-terminal-amber">›</span>
                <span>CSV import/export for test cases</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-terminal-amber">›</span>
                <span>API endpoints for Cypress test automation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-terminal-amber">›</span>
                <span>Attachment support for test evidence</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-terminal-amber">›</span>
                <span>Role-based access control</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hierarchy -->
  <div class="nerv-panel">
    <div class="nerv-panel-header">
      <span>SYSTEM HIERARCHY</span>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6">
      <div class="font-mono text-sm">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-terminal-cyan/50 pl-4 space-y-4">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-terminal-cyan/20 text-terminal-cyan text-xs uppercase border border-terminal-cyan/30">Mission</span>
              <span class="text-terminal-gray">(Project)</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-terminal-gray mt-1 ml-4">Top-level container for all testing activities. Each mission has its own protocol banks and operations.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="ml-6 border-l-2 border-terminal-amber/50 pl-4 space-y-4">
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-terminal-amber/20 text-terminal-amber text-xs uppercase border border-terminal-amber/30">Protocol Bank</span>
                <span class="text-terminal-gray">(Test Suite)</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-terminal-gray mt-1 ml-4">Collection of related test protocols. Group tests by feature, module, or test type.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="ml-6 border-l-2 border-terminal-green/50 pl-4">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-terminal-green/20 text-terminal-green text-xs uppercase border border-terminal-green/30">Protocol</span>
                <span class="text-terminal-gray">(Test Case)</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-terminal-gray mt-1 ml-4">Individual test with preconditions, execution steps, and expected outcomes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="ml-6 border-l-2 border-terminal-red/50 pl-4">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-terminal-red/20 text-terminal-red text-xs uppercase border border-terminal-red/30">Operation</span>
              <span class="text-terminal-gray">(Test Run)</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-terminal-gray mt-1 ml-4">Execution instance of selected protocols. Track pass/fail status and comments for each test.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="ml-6 border-l-2 border-magi-casper/50 pl-4">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-magi-casper/20 text-magi-casper text-xs uppercase border border-magi-casper/30">Deadline</span>
              <span class="text-terminal-gray">(Milestone)</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-terminal-gray mt-1 ml-4">Target dates for mission objectives. Track testing progress against release schedules.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- User Roles -->
  <div class="nerv-panel">
    <div class="nerv-panel-header">
      <span>OPERATOR CLEARANCE LEVELS</span>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="p-4 border border-terminal-red/30">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-3">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-terminal-red/20 text-terminal-red text-xs font-mono uppercase border border-terminal-red/30">
              ADMIN
            </span>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-xs font-mono text-terminal-gray space-y-1">
            <li>• Full system access</li>
            <li>• Manage operators</li>
            <li>• Create/delete missions</li>
            <li>• System configuration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 border border-terminal-amber/30">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-3">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-terminal-amber/20 text-terminal-amber text-xs font-mono uppercase border border-terminal-amber/30">
              MANAGER
            </span>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-xs font-mono text-terminal-gray space-y-1">
            <li>• View all missions</li>
            <li>• Create protocol banks</li>
            <li>• Initialize operations</li>
            <li>• Manage test protocols</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 border border-terminal-cyan/30">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-3">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-terminal-cyan/20 text-terminal-cyan text-xs font-mono uppercase border border-terminal-cyan/30">
              TESTER
            </span>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-xs font-mono text-terminal-gray space-y-1">
            <li>• Execute operations</li>
            <li>• Update test results</li>
            <li>• Add comments/attachments</li>
            <li>• View assigned missions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Quick Actions -->
  <div class="nerv-panel">
    <div class="nerv-panel-header">
      <span>QUICK ACTION GUIDE</span>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 border border-terminal-cyan/30 bg-terminal-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-terminal-cyan font-mono font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-mono text-terminal-white uppercase">Create a Mission</h4>
            <p class="text-xs font-mono text-terminal-gray mt-1">Navigate to Mission Registry and click "Initialize Mission" to start a new project.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 border border-terminal-cyan/30 bg-terminal-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-terminal-cyan font-mono font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-mono text-terminal-white uppercase">Add Protocol Banks</h4>
            <p class="text-xs font-mono text-terminal-gray mt-1">Within your mission, create protocol banks to organize related test cases.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 border border-terminal-cyan/30 bg-terminal-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-terminal-cyan font-mono font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-mono text-terminal-white uppercase">Define Protocols</h4>
            <p class="text-xs font-mono text-terminal-gray mt-1">Add test protocols with preconditions, steps, and expected outcomes. Use CSV import for bulk operations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 border border-terminal-cyan/30 bg-terminal-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-terminal-cyan font-mono font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-mono text-terminal-white uppercase">Execute Operations</h4>
            <p class="text-xs font-mono text-terminal-gray mt-1">Start a test run by selecting protocols to execute. Update status as you complete each test.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 border border-terminal-cyan/30 bg-terminal-cyan/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-terminal-cyan font-mono font-bold">5</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-mono text-terminal-white uppercase">Monitor Progress</h4>
            <p class="text-xs font-mono text-terminal-gray mt-1">Track testing progress on the Command Overview dashboard. View pass/fail metrics and completion percentages.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
